<P>
I am in total agreement with Tara Dawn Wadlington (Viewers' Views, Sept. 3). I 
too feel that "Love Connection" ought to match up individuals of different 
races. The dates then might be more enjoyable for both the participants and the 
audience. I am definitely voting for cross-race dating on "Love Connection." 
</P>
<P>
Terri Alynne Epstein, Los Angeles 
</P>
