<HEADLINE>
<P>
HEY, SOME OF THESE PEOPLE ARE FAMOUS FOR REAL REASONS TOO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Your in-depth report (on "Famous for Being Famous") failed to mention Angelique 
(I think that's her name) -- the Hollywood poster bimbo. 
</P>
<P>
I remember reading or hearing somewhere that she has a manager to make her 
famous. She's not an actress, not a major league ball player and doesn't 
endorse a product to my knowledge. But she's aspiring to be famous. 
</P>
<P>
What a country! 
</P>
<P>
MICHAEL B. BRISON, San Diego 
</P>
