Biological Field Station at the Claremont Colleges. MARILYN WEISS / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Bill Havert, top, of the San Gorgonio chapter of the Sierra Club, 
defender of the Riverside fairy shrimp. LARRY GUS / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Center, Michael Packard, president of Lane/Kuhn Pacific Communities, near the 
site where the shrimp will be protected. ROBERT FAABORG / Los Angeles Times; 
Drawing, SPECIES AT THE BRINK, JAMES OWENS / Los Angeles Times 
