<P>
BOY SHOT WHILE FATHER WAS TESTING A GUN DIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MIAMI 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A 9-year-old boy died early Saturday from wounds suffered when he was shot in 
the head by his father, who was testing a gun for a friend in another room and 
apparently did not know it was loaded. The bullet from a .357 magnum crashed 
through a wall, ricocheted off some furniture and hit the boy Thursday night. 
</P>
