<TEXT>
<P>
Norte Vista 14, Rancho Alamitos 7 -- Clint Jordan scored on a 22-yard pass from 
Ron Poindexter in the first quarter, and Frank Ruiz scored on a 1-yard run in 
the second quarter to lead the hosts at Riverside City College. 
</P>
<P>
Dana Ruiz scored on a 14-yard run in the fourth quarter for Rancho Alamitos 
(1-2). Norte Vista improved its record to 2-1 with the victory. 
</P>
